How to handle PREFIX/share/joomla/installation? That directory MUST be
removed after initial configuration.

How to handle PREFIX/share/joomla/configuration.php? That file contains
the local settings. Maybe take a look at squirrelmail how it keeps
PREFIX/share/squirrelmail/config/config.php out of PLIST.

How to handle PREFIX/share/joomla/tmp, PREFIX/share/joomla/cache and
PREFIX/share/joomla/administrator/cache? Most likely these should be
somewhere in /var (e.g. /var/joomla).
